overview.en: MINI Chain aims to build a huge DApp ecosystem and develop a high-performance block chain ecological bottom platform with high versatility, expansibility and compatibility, which can realize a million-level TPS, universal language development intelligent contract and visualization operation block chain 3.0 pilot project.
overview.zh: MINI Chain旨在打造一个庞大的DApp生态，开发一个通用性、扩展性、兼容性极强的高性能区块链生态底层平台，可实现百万级TPS、通用语言开发智能合约、可视化操作的区块链3.0领航项目。
